صحیح کنید یا ftp client.','Cannot update .htaccess'=>'امکان بروز رسانی فایل .htaccess نمیباشد','WP Super Cache has checked the front page of your blog. Please visit %s if you would like to disable this.'=>'WP Super Cache صفحه نخست شما را بررسی کرد. لطفا مشاهده کنید %s اگر می خواهید این را غیرفعال کنید.','[%s] Front page check!'=>'[%s] بررسی صفحه اول!','The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is missing the text "%2$s". Please visit %1$s to verify the cache has been cleared.'=>'کش موجود در بلاگ شما پاکسازی شد چون صفحه نخست سایت شما متن گمشده "%2$s" دارد. مشاهده کنید  %1$s برای تائید پاکسازی کش.','[%s] Front page is not correct! Cache Cleared!'=>'[%s] صفحه نخست صحیح نیست!کش پاکسازی شد!','Please visit %1$s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is not correct and missing the text, "%2$s"!'=>'مشاهده کنید %1$s برای پاکسازی کش از صفحه نخست سایت شما درست نیست و گمشده متن، "%2$s"!','[%s] Front page is not correct! Please clear cache!'=>'[%s] صفحه نخست صحیح نیست، کش را پاک کنید.','The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is now downloading. Please visit %s to verify the cache has been cleared.'=>'کش در سایت ما پاکسازی شد چون صفحه نخست سایت شما درحال دانلود است. مشاهده کنید %s برای تائید پاکسازی کش.','[%s] Front page is gzipped! Cache Cleared!'=>'[%s] صفحه نخست gzipped شده است، کش را پاکسازی کنید.','Please visit %s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is now downloading!'=>'مشاهده کنید %s برای پاکسازی کش از صفحه نخست سایت شما که در حال دانلود است!','[%s] Front page is gzipped! Please clear cache!'=>'[%s] صفحه نخست gzipped است. کش را پاک کنید','Warning! WP Super Cache caching <strong>was</strong> broken but has been <strong>fixed</strong>! The script advanced-cache.php could not load wp-cache-phase1.php.<br /><br />The file %1$s/advanced-cache.php has been recreated and WPCACHEHOME fixed in your wp-config.php. Reload to hide this message.'=>'Warning! WP Super Cache caching <strong>was</strong> broken but has been <strong>fixed</strong>! The script advanced-cache.php could not load wp-cache-phase1.php.<br /><br />The file %1$s/advanced-cache.php has been recreated and WPCACHEHOME fixed in your wp-config.php. Reload to hide this message.','WP Super Cache is disabled. Please go to the <a href="%s">plugin admin page</a> to enable caching.'=>'WP Super Cache غیرفعال است.به <a href="%s">برگه مدیریت افزونه</a> بروید و فعال کنید.','Settings'=>'تنظیمات','WP Super Cache must be configured. Go to <a href="%s">the admin page</a> to enable and configure the plugin.'=>'افزونه WP Super Cache باید پیکربندی شود. بروید به <a href="%s">برگه مدیریت</a> برای فعالسازی و پیکربندی افزونه.','Delete Super Cache cached files (opens in new window)'=>'حذف پرونده های کش Super Cache (بازکردن در پنجره جدید)','Delete Expired'=>'حذف منقضی شده ها','Expired files are files older than %s seconds. They are still used by the plugin and are deleted periodically.'=>'پرونده های منقضی شده پرونده هایی قدیمی تر از %s ثانیه. آن ها هنوز بکار می برند افزونه و حذف می شوند با همان دوره معین.','List all cached files'=>'فهرست تمام فایل های کش شده','Too many cached files, no listing possible.'=>'پرونده های کش زیاد است،لیست کردنشان ممکن نیست.','Hide file list'=>'مخفی کردن لیست پرونده','Delete'=>'حذف','Age'=>'مدت','URI'=>'آدرس','WP-Super-Cache'=>'افزونه WP Super Cache','%s Expired Pages'=>'%s برگه های منقضی شده','%s Cached Pages'=>'%s برگه های کش شده','WP-Cache'=>'افزونه کش','Cache stats last generated: %s minutes ago.'=>'آمار آخرین کش تولید شده: %s دقیقه قبل.','Regenerate cache stats'=>'تولید مجدد آمار کش','Cache stats are not automatically generated. You must click the link below to regenerate the stats on this page.'=>'آمار کش بطور خودکار تولید نشده است. شما باید لینک زیر را کلیککنید برای بازتولید آمار در این برگه.','Deleting wp-cache file: <strong>%s</strong><br />'=>'حذف پرونده wp-cache: <strong>%s</strong><br />','Deleting supercache file: <strong>%s</strong><br />'=>'حذف پرونده supercache :<strong>%s</strong><br />','Cache Contents'=>'محتوای کش','Edit <code>%s</code> and add the following line:<br /> <code>define(\'WP_CACHE\', true);</code><br />Otherwise, <strong>WP-Cache will not be executed</strong> by WordPress core. '=>'ویرایش <code>%s</code> و خط زیر را اضافه کنید:<br /> <code>define(\'WP_CACHE\', true);</code><br />به بیان دیگر:<strong>WP-Cache اجرا نمی شود</strong> توسط هسته وردپرس. ','<strong>Error: WP_CACHE is not enabled</strong> in your <code>wp-config.php</code> file and I couldn&#8217;t modify it.'=>'<strong>خطا: WP_CACHE فعال نیست</strong>در فایل<code>wp-config.php</code>و نمی توان تغییر داد.','If that doesn&#8217;t work, make sure the file <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em> doesn&#8217;t exist:'=>'اگر کار نکرد، مطمئن شوید پرونده<em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em>وجود ندارد:','Refresh this page to update <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em>'=>'تازه سازی این برگه با بروزرسانی <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em>','Make %1$s writable using the chmod command through your ftp or server software. (<em>chmod 777 %1$s</em>) and refresh this page. This is only a temporary measure and you&#8217;ll have to make it read only afterwards again. (Change 777 to 755 in the previous command)'=>'2. Make %1$s writable using the chmod command through your ftp or server software. (<em>chmod 777 %1$s</em>) and refresh this page. This is only a temporary measure and you&#8217;ll have to make it read only afterwards again. (Change 777 to 755 in the previous command)','Could not update %s!</em> WPCACHEHOME must be set in config file.'=>'نمی تواند بروزرسانی شود%s!</em> WPCACHEHOME باید در پرونده پیکربندی تنظیم شود.','Sample WP-Cache config file (<strong>%s</strong>) does not exist. Verify your installation.'=>'مثال پیکربندی پرونده WP-Cache (<strong>%s</strong>) وجود ندارد. بررسی نصب و راه اندازی.','Configuration file missing and %1$s  directory (<strong>%2$s</strong>) is not writable by the web server. Check its permissions.'=>'پرونده پیکربندی ازدست رفته دایرکتوری %1$s(<strong>%2$s</strong>) قابل بازنویسی نیست توسط سرور. دسترسی ها را بررسی کنید.','Your WP-Cache config file (<strong>%s</strong>) is out of date and not writable by the Web server. Please delete it and refresh this page.'=>'پرونده پیکربندی WP-Cache(<strong>%s</strong>)  منقضی شده است و قابل بازنویسی توسط سرور نیست. لطفا آن را حذف کنید و برگه را تازه سازی نمایید.','Your cache directory (<strong>%1$s</strong>) or <strong>%2$s</strong> need to be writable for this plugin to work. Double-check it.'=>'کش دایرکتوری شما (<strong>%1$s</strong>) یا <strong>%2$s</strong> نیاز به بازنویسی برای کارکرد این افزونه دارد. مجدد بررسی کنید.','Your cache directory (<strong>%1$s</strong>) did not exist and couldn&#8217;t be created by the web server. Check %1$s permissions.'=>'کش دایرکتوری شما (<strong>%1$s</strong>) وجود ندارد و نیم تواند توسط سرور ایجاد شود. بررسی کنید سطح دسترسی های %1$s.','Error'=>'خطا','GZIP compression is enabled in WordPress, wp-cache will be bypassed until you disable gzip compression.'=>'فشرده سازی GZIP فعال است در وردپرس،wp-cache درکنار قرار میگیرد تا هنگامی که شما غیرفعال کنید فشرده سازی gzip.','Warning'=>'هشدار','Email the blog admin when checks are made. (useful for testing)'=>'ایمیل مدیر وبلاگ که بررسی ساخته شده است. (مفید برای تست)','Clear cache on error.'=>'پاک کردن کش در صورت خطا.','Text to search for on your front page. If this text is missing, the cache will be cleared. Leave blank to disable.'=>'متن به جستجو برای صفحه نخست سایت شما. اگر این متن حذف شده،کش پاکسازی می شود. خالی رها کنید تا غیرفعال شود.','Front page text'=>'متن صفحه نخست','Check front page every 5 minutes.'=>'بررسی صفحه نخست هر 5 دقیقه.','I&#8217;m 99% certain that they aren&#8217;t bugs in WP Super Cache and they only happen in very rare cases but you can run a simple check once every 5 minutes to verify that your site is ok if you&#8217;re worried. You will be emailed if there is a problem.'=>'I&#8217;m 99% certain that they aren&#8217;t bugs in WP Super Cache and they only happen in very rare cases but you can run a simple check once every 5 minutes to verify that your site is ok if you&#8217;re worried. You will be emailed if there is a problem.','In very rare cases two problems may arise on some blogs:<ol><li> The front page may start downloading as a zip file.</li><li> The wrong page is occasionally cached as the front page if your blog uses a static front page and the permalink structure is <em>/%category%/%postname%/</em>.</li></ol>'=>'In very rare cases two problems may arise on some blogs:<ol><li> The front page may start downloading as a zip file.</li><li> The wrong page is occasionally cached as the front page if your blog uses a static front page and the permalink structure is <em>/%category%/%postname%/</em>.</li></ol>','Display comments at the end of every page like this:'=>'نمایش دیدگاه ها در انتهای هر برگه بصورت زیر:','Cache Status Messages'=>'پیام‌های وضعیت کش','(only log requests from this IP address. Your IP is %s)'=>'(فقط درخواست گزارش از این آدرس آی پی. آی پی شما %s است)','IP Address'=>'آدرس آی پی','Fix problems with the plugin by debugging it here. It will log to a file in your cache directory.'=>'مشکلات را با افزونه حل کنید با اشکال زدن آن در اینجا. این به یک فایل در دایرکتوری کش شما وارد می شود.','Currently logging to: %s'=>'در حال‌حاضر ورود به سیستم با: %s','Save Files'=>'ذخیره پرونده‌ها','Add here those filenames that can be cached, even if they match one of the rejected substring specified above.'=>'افزودن اینجا آن نام پرونده ها که می تواند کش شود، حتی اگر آن ها هماهنگ با زیررشته پذیرفته نشده تعریف شده بالا.','Save Strings'=>'ذخیره رشته ها','Add here strings (not a filename) that forces a page not to be cached. For example, if your URLs include year and you dont want to cache last year posts, it&#8217;s enough to specify the year, i.e. &#8217;/2004/&#8217;. WP-Cache will search if that string is part of the URI and if so, it will not cache that page.'=>'Add here strings (not a filename) that forces a page not to be cached. For example, if your URLs include year and you dont want to cache last year posts, it&#8217;s enough to specify the year, i.e. &#8217;/2004/&#8217;. WP-Cache will search if that string is part of the URI and if so, it will not cache that page.','Save'=>'ذخیره','Author Pages'=>'برگه‌های نویسنده','Search Pages'=>'برگه‌های جستجو','Feeds'=>'خوراک‌ها','Category'=>'دسته:','Tags'=>'برچسب‌ها','Archives'=>'بایگانی‌ها','Home'=>'صفحه اصلی','Front Page'=>'برگه جلویی','Pages'=>'برگه ها','Single Posts'=>'تک نوشته','Do not cache the following page types. See the <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Conditional_Tags">Conditional Tags</a> documentation for a complete discussion on each type.'=>'انواع برگه زیر را کش نکن. ببینید <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Conditional_Tags">برچسب های مشروط</a>مستندات برای بحث کامل در هر نوع.','Save UA Strings'=>'ذخیره رشته‌های UA','Strings in the HTTP &#8217;User Agent&#8217; header that prevent WP-Cache from caching bot, spiders, and crawlers&#8217; requests. Note that super cached files are still sent to these agents if they already exists.'=>'Strings in the HTTP &#8217;User Agent&#8217; header that prevent WP-Cache from caching bot, spiders, and crawlers&#8217; requests. Note that super cached files are still sent to these agents if they already exists.','Rejected User Agents'=>'رد کردن عوامل کاربر','Change Expiration'=>'تغییر تاریخ انقضاء','Set the expiry time to 0 seconds to disable garbage collection.'=>'تنظیم زمان ابطال به 0 ثانیه برای غیرفعال سازی کالکشن زباله.','Sites where an external data source updates at a particular time every day should set the timeout to 86400 seconds and use the Clock scheduler set appropriately.'=>'Sites where an external data source updates at a particular time every day should set the timeout to 86400 seconds and use the Clock scheduler set appropriately.','Sites with lots of static content, no widgets or rss feeds in their sidebar can use a timeout of 86400 seconds or even more and set the timer to something equally long.'=>'Sites with lots of static content, no widgets or rss feeds in their sidebar can use a timeout of 86400 seconds or even more and set the timer to something equally long.','Sites with widgets and rss feeds in their sidebar should probably use a timeout of 3600 seconds and set the timer to 600 seconds. Stale files will be caught within 10 minutes of going stale.'=>'Sites with widgets and rss feeds in their sidebar should probably use a timeout of 3600 seconds and set the timer to 600 seconds. Stale files will be caught within 10 minutes of going stale.','Sites that want to serve lots of newly generated data should set the <em>Cache Timeout</em> to 60 and use the <em>Timer</em> scheduler set to 90 seconds.'=>'Sites that want to serve lots of newly generated data should set the <em>Cache Timeout</em> to 60 and use the <em>Timer</em> scheduler set to 90 seconds.','There are no best garbage collection settings but here are a few scenarios. Garbage collection is separate to other actions that clear our cached files like leaving a comment or publishing a post.'=>'There are no best garbage collection settings but here are a few scenarios. Garbage collection is separate to other actions that clear our cached files like leaving a comment or publishing a post.','Or, the <em>Clock</em> scheduler allows the garbage collection to run at specific times. If set to run hourly or twice daily, the garbage collector will be first scheduled for the time you enter here. It will then run again at the indicated interval. If set to run daily, it will run once a day at the time specified.'=>'Or, the <em>Clock</em> scheduler allows the garbage collection to run at specific times. If set to run hourly or twice daily, the garbage collector will be first scheduled for the time you enter here. It will then run again at the indicated interval. If set to run daily, it will run once a day at the time specified.','The <em>Timer</em> scheduler tells the plugin to run the garbage collector at regular intervals. When one garbage collection is done, the next run is scheduled.'=>'The <em>Timer</em> scheduler tells the plugin to run the garbage collector at regular intervals. When one garbage collection is done, the next run is scheduled.','Use the <em>Timer</em> or <em>Clock</em> schedulers to define when the garbage collector should run.'=>'Use the <em>Timer</em> or <em>Clock</em> schedulers to define when the garbage collector should run.','Stale cached files are not removed as soon as they become stale. They have to be removed by the garbage collecter. That is why you have to tell the plugin when the garbage collector should run.'=>'Stale cached files are not removed as soon as they become stale. They have to be removed by the garbage collecter. That is why you have to tell the plugin when the garbage collector should run.','Cached files are fresh for a limited length of time. You can set that time in the <em>Cache Timeout</em> text box on this page.'=>'Cached files are fresh for a limited length of time. You can set that time in the <em>Cache Timeout</em> text box on this page.','<em>Garbage collection</em> is the simple act of throwing out your garbage. For this plugin that would be old or <em>stale</em> cached files that may be out of date. New cached files are described as <em>fresh</em>.'=>'<em>Garbage collection</em> is the simple act of throwing out your garbage. For this plugin that would be old or <em>stale</em> cached files that may be out of date. New cached files are described as <em>fresh</em>.','Garbage Collection'=>'Garbage Collection','Email me when the garbage collection runs.'=>'مرا از طریق ایمیل هنگامی که garbage collection اجرا می شود مطلع کن.','Notification Emails'=>'هشدار از طریق ایمیل','Interval:'=>'فاصله:','Check for stale cached files at this time <strong>(UTC)</strong> or starting at this time every <em>interval</em> below.'=>'Check for stale cached files at this time <strong>(UTC)</strong> or starting at this time every <em>interval</em> below.','HH:MM'=>'HH:MM','Clock:'=>'ساعت:','Timer:'=>'زمان سنج:','Scheduler'=>'زمان بندی','How long should cached pages remain fresh? Set to 0 to disable garbage collection. A good starting point is 3600 seconds.'=>'How long should cached pages remain fresh? Set to 0 to disable garbage collection. A good starting point is 3600 seconds.','seconds'=>'ثانیه','Cache Timeout'=>'انقضای کش','Warning! <strong>PRELOAD MODE</strong> activated. Supercache files will not be deleted regardless of age.'=>'Warning! <strong>PRELOAD MODE</strong> activated. Supercache files will not be deleted regardless of age.','Next scheduled garbage collection will be at <strong>%s UTC</strong>'=>'Next scheduled garbage collection will be at <strong>%s UTC</strong>','Local time is <code>%1$s</code>'=>'زمان محلی <code>%1$s</code>','<abbr title="Coordinated Universal Time">UTC</abbr> time is <code>%s</code>'=>'<abbr title="Coordinated Universal Time">UTC</abbr> time is <code>%s</code>','Expiry Time &amp; Garbage Collection'=>'زمان ابطال &amp; کالکشن زباله','timezone date formatY-m-d G:i:s'=>'Y-m-d G:i:s','Update Direct Pages'=>'برگه های مستقیم بروز شد','Make the textbox blank to remove it from the list of direct pages and delete the cached file.'=>'Make the textbox blank to remove it from the list of direct pages and delete the cached file.','For example: to cache <em>%1$sabout/</em>, you would enter %1$sabout/ or /about/. The cached file will be generated the next time an anonymous user visits that page.'=>'For example: to cache <em>%1$sabout/</em>, you would enter %1$sabout/ or /about/. The cached file will be generated the next time an anonymous user visits that page.','Directly cached files are files created directly off %s where your blog lives. This feature is only useful if you are expecting a major Digg or Slashdot level of traffic to one post or page.'=>'Directly cached files are files created directly off %s where your blog lives. This feature is only useful if you are expecting a major Digg or Slashdot level of traffic to one post or page.','Add direct page:'=>'اضافه کردن برگه مستقیم:','Delete cached file'=>'حذف فایل کش شده','Existing direct page'=>'برگه مستقیم موجود','%s is writable. Please make it readonly after your page is generated as this is a security risk.'=>'%s is writable. Please make it readonly after your page is generated as this is a security risk.','You must make %s writable to enable this feature. As this is a security risk, please make it read-only after your page is generated.'=>'You must make %s writable to enable this feature. As this is a security risk, please make it read-only after your page is generated.','Directly Cached Files'=>'فایلهایی که مستقیم کش شده','Lock Down'=>'مستند','WordPress is not locked down. New comments will refresh Super Cache static files as normal.'=>'WordPress is not locked down. New comments will refresh Super Cache static files as normal.','WordPress is locked down. Super Cache static files will not be deleted when new comments are made.'=>'WordPress is locked down. Super Cache static files will not be deleted when new comments are made.','Sorry. My blog is locked down. Updates will appear shortly'=>'Sorry. My blog is locked down. Updates will appear shortly','Developers: Make your plugin lock down compatible by checking the "WPLOCKDOWN" constant. The following code will make sure your plugin respects the WPLOCKDOWN setting.'=>'Developers: Make your plugin lock down compatible by checking the "WPLOCKDOWN" constant. The following code will make sure your plugin respects the WPLOCKDOWN setting.','Prepare your server for an expected spike in traffic by enabling the lock down. When this is enabled, new comments on a post will not refresh the cached static files.'=>'Prepare your server for an expected spike in traffic by enabling the lock down. When this is enabled, new comments on a post will not refresh the cached static files.','Lock Down:'=>'قفل کردن:','Comment moderation is enabled. Your comment may take some time to appear.'=>'تائید دیدگاه فعال است. دیدگاه شما ممکن است کمی طول بکشد تا ظاهر شود.','Restore Default Configuration'=>'بازگشت به حالت اولیه پیکربندی','Fix Configuration'=>'تعمیر پیکربندی','Rules must be added to %s too:'=>'قوانین باید اضافه شود به %s همچنین:','View Mod_Rewrite Rules'=>'دیدن قوانین Mod_Rewrite','A difference between the rules in your .htaccess file and the plugin rewrite rules has been found. This could be simple whitespace differences, but you should compare the rules in the file with those below as soon as possible. Click the &#8217;Update Mod_Rewrite Rules&#8217; button to update the rules.'=>'A difference between the rules in your .htaccess file and the plugin rewrite rules has been found. This could be simple whitespace differences, but you should compare the rules in the file with those below as soon as possible. Click the &#8217;Update Mod_Rewrite Rules&#8217; button to update the rules.','WP Super Cache mod rewrite rules were detected in your %s.htaccess file.<br /> Click the following link to see the lines added to that file. If you have upgraded the plugin, make sure these rules match.'=>'WP Super Cache mod rewrite rules were detected in your %s.htaccess file.<br /> Click the following link to see the lines added to that file. If you have upgraded the plugin, make sure these rules match.','Mod Rewrite rules must be updated!'=>'حالت بازنویسی قوانین باید بروزشود','%s.htaccess has been updated with the necessary mod_rewrite rules. Please verify they are correct. They should look like this:'=>'%s.htaccess has been updated with the necessary mod_rewrite rules. Please verify they are correct. They should look like this:','Mod Rewrite rules updated!'=>'حالت بازنویسی قوانین بروز شد','The mod_rewrite rules changed since you last installed this plugin. Unfortunately, you must remove the old supercache rules before the new ones are updated. Refresh this page when you have edited your .htaccess file. If you wish to manually upgrade, change the following line: %1$s so it looks like this: %2$s The only changes are "HTTP_COOKIE" becomes "HTTP:Cookie" and "wordpressuser" becomes "wordpress". This is a WordPress 2.5 change but it&#8217;s backwards compatible with older versions if you&#8217;re brave enough to use them.'=>'The mod_rewrite rules changed since you last installed this plugin. Unfortunately, you must remove the old supercache rules before the new ones are updated. Refresh this page when you have edited your .htaccess file. If you wish to manually upgrade, change the following line: %1$s so it looks like this: %2$s The only changes are "HTTP_COOKIE" becomes "HTTP:Cookie" and "wordpressuser" becomes "wordpress". This is a WordPress 2.5 change but it&#8217;s backwards compatible with older versions if you&#8217;re brave enough to use them.','Thank you for upgrading.'=>'تشکر بابت ارتقاء پلاگین.','Mod Rewrite Rules'=>'قوانین Mod Rewrite','Debug'=>'حالت اشکال زادیی','Plugins'=>'پلاگین ها','Preload'=>'پیش بارگزاری','Contents'=>'محتویات','CDN'=>'CDN','Easy'=>'آسان','Available Plugins'=>'افزونه های موجود','(may not always be accurate on busy sites)'=>'(ممکن است همیشه در سایت های شلوغ دقیق نباشد.)','Cached %s seconds ago'=>'کش شده در %s ثانیه پیش','Newest Cached Pages:'=>'جدیدترین صفحات کش شده:','Cached pages since %1$s : <strong>%2$s</strong>'=>'Cached pages since %1$s : <strong>%2$s</strong>','Rate This Plugin'=>'به این افزونه امتیاز دهید','Need Help?'=>'به کمک نیاز دارید؟','<a href="%s">WP Crontrol</a> is a useful plugin to use when trying to debug garbage collection and preload problems.'=>'<a href="%s">WP Control</a> is a useful plugin to use when trying to debug garbage collection and preload problems.','Caching is only one part of making a website faster. Here are some other plugins that will help:'=>'کش کردن تنها بخشی از کاری است که باعث بالارفتن سرعت سایت می شود.اینجا می توانید افزونه های دیگری دراین باره را ببینید:','Recommended Links and Plugins'=>'پیوندها و افزونه های توصیه شده','Delete Cache On All Blogs'=>'حذف کش از همه بلاگ ها','Delete Cache'=>'حذف کش','Cached pages are stored on your server as html and PHP files. If you need to delete them, use the button below.'=>'برگه های کش ذخیره شده در سرور شما بعنوان فایل های html و PHP.اگر نیاز دارید حذفشان کنید. از دکمه زیر استفاده کنید.','Delete Cached Pages'=>'حذف برگه های کش شده','Test Cache'=>'تست کش','Send non-secure (non https) request for homepage'=>'ارسال ناامن(non https) درخواست برای صفحه اصلی','You should check Page 1 and Page 2 above for errors. Your local server configuration may not allow your website to access itself.'=>'شما باید برگه 1 و برگه 2 را بررسی کنید برای خطا.پیکربندی سرور محلی شما ممکن است اجازه ندهد به سایت شما دسترسی دهد.','Enable logging on the Debug page here. That should help you track down the problem.'=>'فعال کردن ورود در برگه اشکال زدایی. که باید به شما کمک کند مشکل را رهگیری کنید.','Load your homepage in a logged out browser, check the timestamp at the end of the html source. Load the page again and compare the timestamp. Caching is working if the timestamps match.'=>'بارگذاری صفحه اصلی شما در هنگام خارج شدن.بررسی برچسب زمان در پایان منبع html. بارگذاری مجدد برگه و مقایسه برچسب زمان.کش کردن کار می کند اگر برچسب های زمانی یکسان باشند.','Things you can do:'=>'چیزهایی که می توانید انجام دهید:','The pages do not match! Timestamps differ or were not found!'=>'برگه ها یکسان نیستند. برچسب زمانی متفاوت است یا یافت نمی شود.','The timestamps on both pages match!'=>'برچسب های زمانی در هردوبرگه یسکان هستند.','Page 2: %s'=>'برگه 2: %s','Page 1: %s'=>'برگه 1: %s','Page %d: %d (%s)'=>'برگه %d: %d (%s)','Fetching second copy of %s: '=>'واکشی کپی دوم از %s: ','FAILED'=>'ناموفق','Fetching first copy of %s: '=>'واکشی کپی اول از %s: ','OK'=>'تایید','Fetching %s to prime cache: '=>'واکشی %s کش اصلی: ','Test your cached website by clicking the test button below.'=>'کش سایت خود را تست کنید با کلیک روی دکمه زیر.','Cache Tester'=>'آزمایش کش','Notice: Simple caching enabled but Supercache mod_rewrite rules from expert mode detected. Cached files will be served using those rules. If your site is working ok, please ignore this message. Otherwise, you can edit the .htaccess file in the root of your install and remove the SuperCache rules.'=>'Notice: PHP caching enabled but Supercache mod_rewrite rules detected. Cached files will be served using those rules. If your site is working ok, please ignore this message. Otherwise, you can edit the .htaccess file in the root of your install and remove the SuperCache rules.','Caching Off'=>'کش کردن خاموش','Caching On'=>'کش کردن روشن','Accepted Filenames &amp; Rejected URIs'=>'نام پرونده های پذیرفته شده &amp; آدرس های اینترنتی نپذیرفته شده','Update Status'=>'بروزرسانی وضعیت','Please see the <a href="%1$s/wp-super-cache/readme.txt">readme.txt</a> for instructions on uninstalling this script. Look for the heading, "How to uninstall WP Super Cache".'=>'Please see the <a href="%1$s/wp-super-cache/readme.txt">readme.txt</a> for instructions on uninstalling this script. Look for the heading, "How to uninstall WP Super Cache".','If uninstalling this plugin, make sure the directory <em>%s</em> is writeable by the webserver so the files <em>advanced-cache.php</em> and <em>cache-config.php</em> can be deleted automatically. (Making sure those files are writeable is probably a good idea!)'=>'If uninstalling this plugin, make sure the directory <em>%s</em> is writeable by the webserver so the files <em>advanced-cache.php</em> and <em>cache-config.php</em> can be deleted automatically. (Making sure those files are writeable is probably a good idea!)','Uninstall this plugin on the plugins page. It will automatically clean up after itself. If manual intervention is required, then simple instructions are provided.'=>'حذف این افزونه در برگه افزونه ها. بطور خودکار پاکسازی می کند.اگر کار دستی نیاز بود آن وقت راهکاری ساده ارائه می شود.','Note:'=>'یادداشت:','<strong>DO NOT CACHE PAGE</strong> secret key: <a href="%s">%s</a>'=>'<strong>کش نکن برگه را</strong> کلید امنیتی: <a href="%s">%s</a>','List the newest cached pages on this page.'=>'لیست برگه های کش شده جدید در این صفحه.','Only refresh current page when comments made.'=>'فقط تازه سازی کنید برگه کنونی را وقتی که شامل دیدگاه باشد.','Extra homepage checks. (Very occasionally stops homepage caching)'=>'بررسی صفحه اصلی اضافی.(گاهی اوقات توقف کش صفحه اصلی)','Clear all cache files when a post or page is published or updated.'=>'پاکسازی همه پرونده های کش وقتی که نوشته یا برگه ارسال می شود یا بروزرسانی میگردد.','Remove UTF8/blog charset support from .htaccess file. Only necessary if you see odd characters or punctuation looks incorrect. Requires rewrite rules update.'=>'Remove UTF8/blog charset support from .htaccess file. Only necessary if you see odd characters or punctuation looks incorrect. Requires rewrite rules update.','Mobile Prefixes'=>'پیشوندهای موبایل','Mobile Browsers'=>'مرورگر موبایل','Advanced'=>'پیشرفته','Cache rebuild. Serve a supercache file to anonymous users while a new file is being generated.'=>'کش بازسازی شد.بکارگیری پرونده supercache به کاربران ناشناس در حالی که پرونده جدید شروع به ایجاد شدن کرده است.','Make known users anonymous so they&#8217;re served supercached static files.'=>'ساخت کاربران شناخته شده ناشناس که آن ها بکار می برند پرونده های ایستای supercached.','Don&#8217;t cache pages with GET parameters. (?x=y at the end of a url)'=>'برگه های دارای پارامتر GET ررا کش نکن.(?x=y در انتهای آدرس اینترنتی)','304 support is disabled by default because some hosts have had problems with the headers used in the past.'=>'پشتیبانی 304 غیرفعال شد توسط پیشفرض چون برخی میزبانی ها مشکل دارند با سربرگی که بکار رفته است در گذشته.','Compression is disabled by default because some hosts have problems with compressed files. Switching it on and off clears the cache.'=>'مقایسه غیرفعال است توسط پیشفرض چون برخی میزبان ها مشکل دارند با پرونده های فشرده شده. روشن و خاموش کردن پاکسازی کش.','Compress pages so they&#8217;re served more quickly to visitors.'=>'فشرده سازی برگه ها طوری که آن ها سریعتر به مشاهده کنندگان نمایش داده شود.','Warning! Compression is disabled as gzencode() function was not found.'=>'اخطار! فشرده سازی غیرفعال است چون تابع gzencode() یافت نشد.','Miscellaneous'=>'متفرقه','Recommended'=>'پیشنهادی','Caching'=>'کش کردن','Less emails, 1 at the start and 1 at the end of preloading all posts.'=>'ایمیل کمتر، 1 در شروع و 1 در پایان پیش بارگذاری همه نوشته ها.','Send me status emails when files are refreshed.'=>'ارسال کن به من وضعیت ایمیل ها را زمانی که پرونده ها تازه سازی می شود.','Preload tags, categories and other taxonomies.'=>'پیش بارگذاری برچسب ها،دسته ها و دیگر طبقه بندی ها.','Preload %s posts.'=>'پش بارگذاری %s نوشته.','all'=>'همه','Refresh preloaded cache files every %s minutes. (0 to disable, minimum %d minutes.)'=>'تازه سازی پیش بارگذاری پرونده کش هر%s دقیقه.(0 برای غیرفعال شدن،کمترین %d دقیقه.)','Preloading creates lots of files however. Caching is done from the newest post to the oldest so please consider only caching the newest if you have lots (10,000+) of posts. This is especially important on shared hosting.'=>'Preloading creates lots of files however. Caching is done from the newest post to the oldest so please consider only caching the newest if you have lots (10,000+) of posts. This is especially important on shared hosting.','This will cache every published post and page on your site. It will create supercache static files so unknown visitors (including bots) will hit a cached page. This will probably help your Google ranking as they are using speed as a metric when judging websites now.'=>'This will cache every published post and page on your site. It will create supercache static files so unknown visitors (including bots) will hit a cached page. This will probably help your Google ranking as they are using speed as a metric when judging websites now.','Preload Cache Now'=>'اکنون پیش بارگذاری کش','Cancel Cache Preload'=>'کنسل کردن پیش بارگذاری کش','Configuration file changed, some values might be wrong. Load the page again from the "Settings" menu to reset them.'=>'پیکربندی پرونده تعییر یافت ممکن است برخی مقادیر اشتباه باشد. برگه را مجدد بارگذاری کنید از فهرست"تنظیمات" برای تنظیم مجدد آن. ','Notice: <em>Expert mode caching enabled</em>. Showing Advanced Settings Page by default.'=>'Notice: <em>Mod_rewrite or Legacy caching enabled</em>. Showing Advanced Settings Page by default.','<strong>Warning!</strong> You attempted to enable compression but <code>zlib.output_compression</code> is enabled. See #21 in the Troubleshooting section of the readme file.'=>'<strong>Warning!</strong> You attempted to enable compression but <code>zlib.output_compression</code> is enabled. See #21 in the Troubleshooting section of the readme file.','It appears you have WordPress installed in a sub directory as described <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Giving_WordPress_Its_Own_Directory">here</a>. Unfortunately, WordPress writes to the .htaccess in the install directory, not where your site is served from.<br />When you update the rewrite rules in this plugin you will have to copy the file to where your site is hosted. This will be fixed in the future.'=>'It appears you have WordPress installed in a sub directory as described <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Giving_WordPress_Its_Own_Directory">here</a>. Unfortunately, WordPress writes to the .htaccess in the install directory, not where your site is served from.<br />When you update the rewrite rules in this plugin you will have to copy the file to where your site is hosted. This will be fixed in the future.','.htaccess file may need to be moved'=>'پرونده .htaccess باید جابجا شود','The following Apache modules are missing. The plugin will work in simple mode without them but in expert mode, your visitors may see corrupted pages or out of date content however.'=>'The following Apache modules are missing. The plugin will work in legacy mode without them. In full Supercache mode, your visitors may see corrupted pages or out of date content however.','Missing Apache Modules'=>'گم شدن ماژول آپاچی','Set the expiry date on supercached pages. Visitors may not see new pages when they refresh or leave comments without this module.'=>'Set the expiry date on supercached pages. Visitors may not see new pages when they refresh or leave comments without this module.','Required to set caching information on supercache pages. IE7 users will see old pages without this module.'=>'Required to set caching information on supercache pages. IE7 users will see old pages without this module.','Required to serve compressed supercache files properly.'=>'نیازمند همراهی فشرده سازی پرونده های supercache بدرستی.','Add the rules yourself. Edit %s.htaccess and find the block of code enclosed by the lines <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> and <code># END WPSuperCache</code>. There are two sections that look very similar. Just below the line <code>%%{HTTP:Cookie} !^.*(comment_author_|%s|wp-postpass_).*$</code> add these lines: (do it twice, once for each section)'=>'Add the rules yourself. Edit %s.htaccess and find the block of code enclosed by the lines <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> and <code># END WPSuperCache</code>. There are two sections that look very similar. Just below the line <code>%%{HTTP:Cookie} !^.*(comment_author_|%s|wp-postpass_).*$</code> add these lines: (do it twice, once for each section)','Delete the plugin mod_rewrite rules in %s.htaccess enclosed by <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> and <code># END WPSuperCache</code> and let the plugin regenerate them by reloading this page.'=>'Delete the plugin mod_rewrite rules in %s.htaccess enclosed by <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> and <code># END WPSuperCache</code> and let the plugin regenerate them by reloading this page.','Scroll down the Advanced Settings page and click the <strong>Update Mod_Rewrite Rules</strong> button.'=>'پیمایش به پایین برگه تنظیمات پیشرفته و کلیک روی دکمه <strong> بروزرسانی قوانین Mod_Rewrite</strong>.','Set the plugin to simple mode and enable mobile support.'=>'تنظیم افزونهه به حالت قدیمی و فعال سازی پشتیبانی موبایل.','Mobile support requires extra rules in your .htaccess file, or you can set the plugin to simple mode. Here are your options (in order of difficulty):'=>'پشتیبانی موبایل نیازمند قوانین زیادی در پرونده .htaccess شماست یا شما می توانید افزونه را در حالت قدیمی قرار دهید. این است تنظیمات شما ( در مرتب سازی سختی):','The rewrite rules required by this plugin have changed or are missing. '=>'بازنویسی قوانین نیازاست برای این افزونه که تغییر کرده یا گم شده است.','Rewrite rules must be updated'=>'بازنویسی قوانین باید بروزرسانی شود','This will have no affect on ordinary users but mobile users will see uncached pages.'=>'This will have no affect on ordinary users but mobile users will see uncached pages.','For best performance you should enable "Mobile device support" or delete the mobile rewrite rules in your .htaccess. Look for the 2 lines with the text "2.0\\ MMP|240x320" and delete those.'=>'For best performance you should enable "Mobile device support" or delete the mobile rewrite rules in your .htaccess. Look for the 2 lines with the text "2.0\\ MMP|240x320" and delete those.','Mobile rewrite rules detected'=>'بازنویسی قوانین موبایل شناسایی شد','You should change the permissions on %s and make it more restrictive. Use your ftp client, or the following command to fix things:'=>'You should change the permissions on %s and make it more restrictive. Use your ftp client, or the following command to fix things:','Warning! %s is writeable!'=>'اخطار!%s قابل بازنویسی است!','Dismiss'=>'رد کردن','Garbage collection by this plugin clears out expired and old cached pages on a regular basis. Use <a href="#expirytime">this form</a> to enable it.'=>'Garbage collection by this plugin clears out expired and old cached pages on a regular basis. Use <a href="#expirytime">this form</a> to enable it.','Warning! Garbage collection is not scheduled!'=>'اخطار! کالکشن زباله زمانبندی نشده است!','Read-only:'=>'فقط خواندنی:','Writeable:'=>'قابل نوشتن:','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Changing_File_Permissions">This page</a> explains how to change file permissions.'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Changing_File_Permissions">This page</a> explains how to change file permissions.','A simple way of doing that is by changing the permissions temporarily using the CHMOD command or through your ftp client. Make sure it&#8217;s globally writeable and it should be fine.'=>'A simple way of doing that is by changing the permissions temporarily using the CHMOD command or through your ftp client. Make sure it&#8217;s globally writeable and it should be fine.','The WP Super Cache configuration file is <code>%s/wp-cache-config.php</code> and cannot be modified. That file must be writeable by the web server to make any changes.'=>'The WP Super Cache configuration file is <code>%s/wp-cache-config.php</code> and cannot be modified. That file must be writeable by the web server to make any changes.','Read Only Mode. Configuration cannot be changed.'=>'حالت فقط خواندنی. پیکربندی نمی تواند تغییر کند.','It appears that mod_rewrite is not installed. Sometimes this check isn&#8217;t 100% reliable, especially if you are not using Apache. Please verify that the mod_rewrite module is loaded. It is required for serving Super Cache static files in expert mode. You will still be able to simple mode.'=>'It appears that mod_rewrite is not installed. Sometimes this check isn&#8217;t 100% reliable, especially if you are not using Apache. Please verify that the mod_rewrite module is loaded. It is required for serving Super Cache static files. You will still be able to use legacy or PHP modes.','Mod rewrite may not be installed!'=>'حالت بازنویسی ممکن است نصب نشده باشد!','PHP is compressing the data sent to the visitors of your site. Disabling this is recommended as the plugin caches the compressed output once instead of compressing the same page over and over again. Also see #21 in the Troubleshooting section. See <a href="http://php.net/manual/en/zlib.configuration.php">this page</a> for instructions on modifying your php.ini.'=>'PHP is compressing the data sent to the visitors of your site. Disabling this is recommended as the plugin caches the compressed output once instead of compressing the same page over and over again. Also see #21 in the Troubleshooting section. See <a href="http://php.net/manual/en/zlib.configuration.php">this page</a> for instructions on modifying your php.ini.','Zlib Output Compression Enabled!'=>'خروجی فشرده سازی Zlib فعال شد!','Cannot continue... fix previous problems and retry.'=>'نمی تواند ادامه یابد... مشکل قبلی را حل کرده و مجدد اقدام کنید.','Unfortunately, WordPress cannot find the file wp-cron.php. This script is required for the correct operation of garbage collection by this plugin, WordPress scheduled posts as well as other critical activities.'=>'Unfortunately, WordPress cannot find the file wp-cron.php. This script is required for the correct operation of garbage collection by this plugin, WordPress scheduled posts as well as other critical activities.','Please see entry 16 in the <a href="%s">Troubleshooting section</a> of the readme.txt'=>'Please see entry 16 in the <a href="%s">Troubleshooting section</a> of the readme.txt','Your server thinks your hostname resolves to %s. Some services such as garbage collection by this plugin, and WordPress scheduled posts may not operate correctly.'=>'Your server thinks your hostname resolves to %s. Some services such as garbage collection by this plugin, and WordPress scheduled posts may not operate correctly.','Warning! Your hostname "%s" resolves to %s'=>'اخطار! نام میزبانی شما "%s" برطرف شده %s','A custom url or permalink structure is required for this plugin to work correctly. Please go to the <a href="options-permalink.php">Permalinks Options Page</a> to configure your permalinks.'=>'A custom url or permalink structure is required for this plugin to work correctly. Please go to the <a href="options-permalink.php">Permalinks Options Page</a> to configure your permalinks.','Permlink Structure Error'=>'خطای ساختار پیوندیکتا','You or an administrator must disable this. See the <a href="http://php.net/features.safe-mode">safe mode manual page</a> for further details. This cannot be disabled in a .htaccess file unfortunately. It must be done in the php.ini config file.'=>'You or an administrator must disable this. See the <a href="http://php.net/features.safe-mode">safe mode manual page</a> for further details. This cannot be disabled in a .htaccess file unfortunately. It must be done in the php.ini config file.','Your server is set up to check the owner of PHP scripts before allowing them to read and write files.'=>'سرور شما راه اندازی شده برای بررسی اسکریپت های php خود قبل از جازه دادن به پرونده ها برای خواندن و نوشتن.','You may experience problems running this plugin because SAFE MODE is enabled.'=>'You may experience problems running this plugin because SAFE MODE is enabled.','Warning! PHP Safe Mode Enabled!'=>'اخطار! حالت امن PHP فعال است!','Please create %s/wp-cache-config.php from wp-super-cache/wp-cache-config-sample.php'=>'لطفا %s/wp-cache-config.php را از wp-super-cache/wp-cache-config-sample.php ایجاد کنید','[%1$s] WP Super Cache GC Report'=>'[%1$s] گزارش WP Super Cache GC','Cache expiry cron job took more than 30 seconds. You should probably run the garbage collector more often.'=>'Cache expiry cron job took more than 30 seconds. You should probably run the garbage collector more often.','Cache expiry cron job failed. Job will run again in 10 seconds.'=>'ابطال کش cron job شکست خورد. دوباره این عمل اجرا می شود در 10 ثانیه دیگر.','WPTouch plugin detected! Please go to the Supercache plugins page and enable the WPTouch helper plugin.'=>'WPTouch plugin detected! Please go to the Supercache plugins page and enable the WPTouch helper plugin.','WPTouch support is now %s'=>'WPTouch اکنون پشتیبانی می شود %s','Provides support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wptouch/">WPTouch</a> mobile theme and plugin.'=>'Provides support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wptouch/">WPTouch</a> mobile theme and plugin.','WPTouch'=>'افزونه WPTouch','Caching has been disabled on this blog on the Network Admin Sites page.'=>'کش در این سایت در شبکه برگه مدیریت غیرفعال است.','Disable'=>'غیرفعال','Enable'=>'قادر ساختن','Cached'=>'کش شده','Jetpack Mobile Theme support is now %s'=>'Jetpack Mobile Theme support is now %s','Provides support for the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/">Jetpack</a> mobile theme and plugin. PHP caching mode and mobile support will be enabled too.'=>'Provides support for the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/">Jetpack</a> mobile theme and plugin. PHP caching mode and mobile support will be enabled too.','Jetpack not found in %s. Install it and enable the mobile theme and this helper plugin to cache visits by mobile visitors.'=>'Jetpack not found in %s. Install it and enable the mobile theme and this helper plugin to cache visits by mobile visitors.','Jetpack Mobile Theme'=>'قالب موبایل Jetpack','Domain Mapping plugin detected! Please go to the Supercache plugins page and enable the domain mapping helper plugin.'=>'Domain Mapping plugin detected! Please go to the Supercache plugins page and enable the domain mapping helper plugin.','Domain Mapping support is now %s'=>'Domain Mapping support is now %s','Provides support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-mu-domain-mapping/">Domain Mapping</a> plugin to map multiple domains to a blog.'=>'Provides support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-mu-domain-mapping/">Domain Mapping</a> plugin to map multiple domains to a blog.','Domain Mapping'=>'نقشه دامنه','Warning!'=>'هشدار!','Bad Behavior support is now %s'=>'رفتار بد پشتیبانی می شود الان %s','(Only WPCache caching supported, disabled compression and requires <a href="http://www.bad-behavior.ioerror.us/">Bad Behavior</a> in "%s/plugins/bad-behavior/") '=>'(Only legacy caching supported, disabled compression and requires <a href="http://www.bad-behavior.ioerror.us/">Bad Behavior</a> in "%s/plugins/bad-behavior/") ','Bad Behavior'=>'رفتار بد','Bad Behaviour not found. Please check your install.'=>'رفتار بدی یافت نشد. نصب خود را بررسی کنید.','Update'=>'بروزرسانی','Awaiting Moderation is now %s'=>'در انتظار نظارت در حال حاضر %s','disabled'=>'غیرفعال','enabled'=>'فعال','Enables or disables plugin to Remove the text "Your comment is awaiting moderation." when someone leaves a moderated comment.'=>'فعال یا غیرفعال کردن افزونه برای حذف متن "دیدگاه شما در انتظار تائید است." وقتی که کسی دیدگاهی می نویسد.','Disabled'=>'غیرفعال','Enabled'=>'فعال','Awaiting Moderation'=>'در انتظار بررسی','Your comment is awaiting moderation.'=>'دیدگاه شما در منتظر تایید است.','Save Changes'=>'ذخیره‏ی تغییرات','Skip https URLs to avoid "mixed content" errors'=>'ردشدن https URLs برای صرف نظر از خطای "mixed content"','Additional CNAMES'=>'CNAMES اضافی','Excludes something from being rewritten if one of the above strings is found in the URL. Use a comma as the delimiter like this, <code>.php, .flv, .do</code>, and always include <code>.php</code> (default).'=>'Excludes something from being rewritten if one of the above strings is found in the match. Use a comma as the delimiter like this, <code>.php, .flv, .do</code>, and always include <code>.php</code> (default).','Exclude if substring'=>'حذف اگر رشته فرعی باشد','Directories to include in static file matching. Use a comma as the delimiter. Default is <code>wp-content, wp-includes</code>, which will be enforced if this field is left empty.'=>'Directories to include in static file matching. Use a comma as the delimiter. Default is <code>wp-content, wp-includes</code>, which will be enforced if this field is left empty.','Include directories'=>'شامل دایرکتوری ها','The new URL to be used in place of %1$s for rewriting. No trailing <code>/</code> please.<br />Example: <code>%2$s</code>.'=>'The new URL to be used in place of %1$s for rewriting. No trailing <code>/</code> please.<br />Example: <code>%2$s</code>.','Off-site URL'=>'آدرس خارج از سایت','Enable CDN Support'=>'فعال سازی پشتیبانی CDN','You can define different CDN URLs for each site on a multsite network.'=>'می توانید آدرس های cdn متفاوتی برای هر سایت در شبکه چند سایته تعریف کنید.','<strong style="color: red">WARNING:</strong> Test some static urls e.g., %s  to ensure your CDN service is fully working before saving changes.'=>'<strong style="color: red">WARNING:</strong> Test some static urls e.g., %s  to ensure your CDN service is fully working before saving changes.']];